1.0.name: wordpress/kvarken
1.0.description: A responsive customizable theme that works out of the box. -Leave the options as is or go wild and change them all! Two widget areas, header image and menu placement, logo upload, sticky posts, threaded comments and unlimited colors. Change details such as breadcrumb navigation, rounded corners, shadows and icons. Includes several header images related to the Kvarken Archipelago and Swedish translation.
